            <p style="padding-top:20px; text-align:justify;">
                <strong> 25.</strong><span style="padding-left: 30px"><strong><u>METHOD OF  CALCULATION OF  PROPORTIONATE SHARE  
                WHEREVER REFERRED TO IN THEAGREEMENT:</u></strong></span>
